{"tid":1692870,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［突破樽頸］新文宣方法","createTime":"2019-11-04T09:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T09:50:44.000Z","uid":300696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"070fb83f9483de15fa934d6c35d1b65bb7699302","tid":1692870,"uid":300696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:40:58.000Z","msg":"新文宣方法<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">流動文宣！！！</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">戴個頭盔，唔係小弟諗，純宣傳。</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">做法</span><br />\n1.去文宣channel搵文宣<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=yqGHcbR114BEm%2FDIyWJWfpMONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=4937c671\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n<br />\n2.印A4 size，建議雙面，反轉就係另外一張<br />\n<br />\n3.痴落自己個袋度，最簡單可以就咁用膠紙嗰D痴，但係會冇咁穩陣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KncC1us.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKncC1us.jpg&h=a09696d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟自己咁做，用兩個扣針扣起，唔會跌，就算比人扯都係爛紙，唔會傷袋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">好處</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">安全</span></span>，有特別情況一扯就變返普通人，重新整過都勁快。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">極和平</span></span>，整連儂牆可以比人告刑事毀壞，呢個應該真冇犯法<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">宣傳效果好</span></span>過連儂牆，連儂牆而家大部分人直行直過，唔會停低睇。但係流動文宣係同D人一齊行緊，唔使特登停低睇，會多D人留意。<br />\n<br />\n再ff下成條街D人都係咁，成件事幾eye catching<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推到成條街都係流動文宣<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"4166f8ae1f047665bee86e4eeddd72fbcb61ab75","tid":1692870,"uid":300696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-04T09:41:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e89026306aa1